1626
01:10:14,560 --> 01:10:15,040
 šta ste,

1627
01:10:15,040 --> 01:10:16,140
 Srbi nije bitno.

1628
01:10:18,020 --> 01:10:18,580
 ali ste,

1629
01:10:18,580 --> 01:10:21,360
 hoćete da ste Amerikanac,

1630
01:10:21,360 --> 01:10:23,060
 ali ne možete ni to,

1631
01:10:23,060 --> 01:10:24,780
