1632
01:10:24,780 --> 01:10:26,460
 Dođete ovdje,

1633
01:10:26,460 --> 01:10:27,620
 ovdje ste Amerikanac.

1634
01:10:27,620 --> 01:10:31,100
 Neko koje nešto pobjeg o tišo,

1635
01:10:31,100 --> 01:10:32,240
