1636
01:10:32,240 --> 01:10:33,520
 nego neko ljut čak.

1637
01:10:33,520 --> 01:10:35,560
 Sada ti me je došao pametava tu iz Amerike.

1638
01:10:35,560 --> 01:10:39,540
 Ak ti misliš da sad je došao pametava,

1639
01:10:39,540 --> 01:10:41,620
 onda ja i ti ne treba da pričam,

1640
01:10:41,620 --> 01:10:42,200
 ne surađujem.

1641
01:10:42,200 --> 01:10:42,940
 Čim je to tako?

1642
01:10:42,940 --> 01:10:44,040
 Važava ruka, čao.

1643
01:10:44,040 --> 01:10:45,840
 Tako da,

1644
01:10:47,000 --> 01:10:48,940
 postoji velika razlika

1645
01:10:48,940 --> 01:10:51,440
 u toj mekoći pristupu,

1646
01:10:51,440 --> 01:10:52,960
 patriotizmu,

1647
01:10:52,960 --> 01:10:54,980
 pristupu,

1648
01:10:54,980 --> 01:10:57,040
 domoljublju,

1649
01:10:57,040 --> 01:10:58,420
 kazao bih.

1650
01:10:58,420 --> 01:11:02,540
 Sada je li to dobro ili loše?

1651
01:11:02,540 --> 01:11:03,860
 To ne mogu ja da kažem.

1652
01:11:03,860 --> 01:11:05,300
 Mislim, je li misliš da,

1653
01:11:05,300 --> 01:11:08,680
 znaš ovaj primjer što si spomenuo,

1654
01:11:08,680 --> 01:11:09,720
 teme koće,

1655
01:11:09,720 --> 01:11:12,200
 kod Amerikanaca i neke njinja osti,

1656
01:11:12,200 --> 01:11:13,920
 njanja osti, kako god to nazvali,

1657
01:11:13,920 --> 01:11:15,520
 je li to,

1658
01:11:15,980 --> 01:11:19,220
