1659
01:11:19,220 --> 01:11:20,720
 A je li to neiskrenost?

1660
01:11:20,720 --> 01:11:22,520
 To je njihov način operatiranja,

1661
01:11:22,520 --> 01:11:24,000
 tako priča čita svoj život.

1662
01:11:24,800 --> 01:11:26,260
 ko kaže da je to neiskreno?

1663
01:11:26,260 --> 01:11:28,580
 Ali ko kaže da smo mi hladni?

1664
