1676
01:11:52,380 --> 01:11:54,840
 Ja ne kažem za svoj narod da je hladen.

1677
01:11:54,840 --> 01:11:56,080
 Nije hladen,

1678
01:11:56,080 --> 01:11:56,840
 nije točno da je hladen.

1679
01:11:56,840 --> 01:11:57,440
 Mislim, smo mi,

1680
01:11:57,440 --> 01:11:58,980
 Bosna, Herzegovna, Hrvatska,

1681
01:11:59,080 --> 01:12:00,460
 Srbija, Crna Gora, Slovenija,

1682
01:12:00,460 --> 01:12:01,600
 Eksiju države.

1683
01:12:01,600 --> 01:12:03,880
 Mislim, smo mi najstračaniji narod.

1684
01:12:03,880 --> 01:12:05,800
 Mi smo toliko strastani,

1685
01:12:05,800 --> 01:12:07,620
 šim...

1686
01:12:07,620 --> 01:12:08,180
 U svemu.

1687
01:12:08,180 --> 01:12:09,000
 Druži u svemu.

1688
01:12:09,000 --> 01:12:09,480
 Tako je.

1689
01:12:09,480 --> 01:12:11,260
