01:14:56,060 --> 01:14:56,920
 One,

1795
01:14:56,920 --> 01:14:58,220
 kik, kik, kik, kik.

1796
01:14:58,220 --> 01:14:59,780
 Druže, dragi,

1797
01:14:59,780 --> 01:15:00,540
 znači,

1798
01:15:00,540 --> 01:15:01,800
 ajmo,

1799
01:15:01,800 --> 01:15:02,880
 opušten, opušten,

1800
01:15:02,880 --> 01:15:03,660
 znači,

1801
